text.*:
The discography of the Eurovision Song Contest winners includes all the winning singles of the annual competition held since 1956. As of May 2018, 66 songs have won the competition, including four entries which were declared joint winners in 1969.

Contents

  • 1 1956–1969
  • 2 1970–1989
  • 3 1990–2009
  • 4 2010–present
  • 5 See also
  • 6 References
